@startuml
title Topología de Backups — E-Commerce + Dashboard

node "Prod Server (Ubuntu 24.04)" {
  [FastAPI/API]
  [Celery Worker]
  database "MySQL 8.4.7" as DB
  queue "Redis 7.4.6" as R
  [Nginx]
}

folder "Backups (Primario)" as B1
cloud "Offsite (Región Alterna)" as OFF

DB -down-> B1 : Full Dump Diario (AES-256)
DB -down-> B1 : Binlogs ≤15m (AES-256)
R -down-> B1 : RDB Diario (AES-256)
[Infra Configs] -down-> B1 : Tarball Semanal

B1 -right-> OFF : Replicación Cifrada + Retención

@enduml
